criteria.description:
POST /api/conversations/{id}/messages responds with Content-Type: text/event-stream; the response body contains one or more SSE data frames in the format 'data: {token}

'; the stream ends with a terminal frame of 'data: [DONE]

' or the connection closes cleanly (no hanging open streams); the concatenated token content (excluding the terminal frame) is a non-empty string when queried against seeded video topics
